  "definition": "Neuroendocrine circuit coordinating the stress response: CRH from hypothalamus → ACTH from pituitary → cortisol from adrenal cortex, with negative feedback.",
  "html": "<div class='ems-body'>\n  <div class='ems-content'>\n    <h3>HPA axis</h3>\n    <p>Neuroendocrine circuit for stress: <strong>CRH → ACTH → cortisol</strong> with negative feedback on both hypothalamus and pituitary.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class='ems-media'>\n    <img class='ems-img' src='https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:HPA_Axis_Diagram_(Brian_M_Sweis_2012).svg#/media/File:HPA_Axis_Diagram_(Brian_M_Sweis_2012).svg' alt='HPA axis diagram'/>\n  </div>\n\n  <table style='width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; margin-top:6px;'>\n    <tr>\n      <td style='border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding:6px;'><strong>Stimuli</strong></td>\n      <td style='border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding:6px;'>Stress, hypoglycemia, circadian rhythm</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style='border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding:6px;'><strong>Sequence</strong></td>\n      <td style='border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding:6px;'>CRH (hypothalamus) → ACTH (anterior pituitary) → Cortisol (adrenal cortex)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style='border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding:6px;'><strong>Feedback</strong></td>\n      <td style='border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding:6px;'>Cortisol suppresses CRH & ACTH release</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <details style='margin-top:8px;'>\n    <summary><strong>High‑yield associations</strong></summary>\n    <ul style='margin:6px 0 0 18px;'>\n      <li>Exogenous steroids → adrenal suppression</li>\n      <li>ACTH‑secreting pituitary adenoma → Cushing disease</li>\n      <li>Primary adrenal failure → ↑ACTH (hyperpigmentation)</li>\n    </ul>\n  </details>\n\n  <div class='ems-actions'>\n    <a class='ems-btn ems-btn--primary' href='https://entermedschool.com' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Watch Lecture</a>\n    <a class='ems-btn ems-btn--secondary' href='https://entermedschool.com' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Read Notes</a>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class='ems-brand'>\n 